{"title":"Reactive declarations","files":[{"name":"App.svelte","source":"<script>\n\tlet count = 1;\n\n\t// the `$:` means 're-run whenever these values change'\n\t$: doubled = count * 2;\n\t$: quadrupled = doubled * 2;\n\n\tfunction handleClick() {\n\t\tcount += 1;\n\t}\n</script>\n\n<button on:click={handleClick}>\n\tCount: {count}\n</button>\n\n<p>{count} * 2 = {doubled}</p>\n<p>{doubled} * 2 = {quadrupled}</p>"}]}